{"tid":1011733,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"港女「影衰」香港人@大和寿司","createTime":"2019-02-07T04:27:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-07T09:33:17.000Z","uid":215883,"like":31,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"e2cd9f190a56107c6290f5305bed78bfc22ad93c","tid":1011733,"uid":215883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:27:35.000Z","msg":"我係last one嗰個客，咁店員都close咗條隊<br />\n條港女自己zip入黎扮朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後被店員發現就話自己係排我前面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就話自己之前去咗洗手間所以遲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講唔掂就問店員識唔識英文&hellip;（明明店員啲英文好勁）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eiPSmXd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeiPSmXd.jpg&h=b0b3a6ec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b66f33a39e08076ead86207b9134a6abb1d91291","tid":1011733,"uid":191815,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:28:34.000Z","msg":"好快連登仔會過嚟屌你係踩港撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓主走先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a25d5d210917042500ded8b01301bbfeb9b3d01","tid":1011733,"uid":61484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:31:35.000Z","msg":"見過類似，壽司大close 左隊放曬牌係隊尾都照排<br />\n<br />\n但冇死撐，應該係睇唔明個牌d 日文"},{"pid":"41c12ea5cd66de2130d15d2f00427b6406885b7a","tid":1011733,"uid":30578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:32:15.000Z","msg":"最後呢"},{"pid":"5ce4869998eb52ee905e0f30310a1f2fae1bd849","tid":1011733,"uid":168366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:32:20.000Z","msg":"睇個樣都港女到爆"},{"pid":"5b05ba8b0dc5634f505a38510242711ad779f1f1","tid":1011733,"uid":71092,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-07T04:38:34.000Z","msg":"樓主